Lyne,
&nbsp;
Fleet Manager will not start without the product identity certificate file (corelight-fleetd.pem) in the /etc directory. This file is required for licensing and sensor communications. &nbsp;To restore the Fleet functionality, you must restore a current Fleet license file (corelight-fleetd.pem) into this directory with the correct file permissions. &nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;
If you do not have a backup of the certificate or if your previous certificate was expired, please let me know and I can request an updated file from the licensing team. &nbsp;If you need any assistance recovering this file, please let me know.
&nbsp;
Thank you,


  Michael Hawks

Senior Escalation Engineer

Corelight 
